@startuml vkb-cli-lifecycle
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam shadowing false

title VKB Server Lifecycle

[*] --> Stopped
Stopped --> Starting : vkb start
Starting --> Running : server ready
Running --> Stopping : vkb stop
Stopping --> Stopped : cleanup complete
Running --> Restarting : vkb restart
Restarting --> Starting : process restart

note right of Starting
  - Port availability check
  - Data preparation
  - Process spawning
  - Health verification
end note

note right of Running
  - HTTP server active
  - Real-time updates
  - Status monitoring
  - Error handling
end note

@enduml